            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note>Text from autopsy. The original full text was reported by Dentici Buccellato after correspondence with Prof. G. Navarra, who originally transcribed the inscription when it was complete.</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="2">
                        <note>The break of the stone appears to follow the downstroke of an 'A' at the beginning of the line. This confirms G. Navarra's original transcription.</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="3">
